    "text": "Ta có: $\\sin 2x = \\frac{\\sqrt{3}}{2} \\Leftrightarrow \\begin{cases} 2x = \\frac{\\pi}{3} + k2\\pi \\\\ 2x = \\frac{2\\pi}{3} + k2\\pi \\end{cases}, k \\in \\mathbb{Z} \\Leftrightarrow \\begin{cases} x = \\frac{\\pi}{6} + k\\pi \\\\ x = \\frac{\\pi}{3} + k\\pi \\end{cases}, k \\in \\mathbb{Z}$."
